{"tid":1844293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隱瞞病情係咪應該坐監","createTime":"2020-01-26T14:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T03:49:33.000Z","uid":224479,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"141c69b83f3b3b49502f96868d5a7f634f9f72a6","tid":1844293,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲大陸人去醫院醫肺炎<br />\n又要瞞撚住自己冇肺炎<br />\n個腦係咪裝屎"},{"pid":"9064e4087fb7b2ca998cd76256b4a35658014c8c","tid":1844293,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:38:02.000Z","msg":"面對咁顛既狗官，同埋黑警不停打壓支持防疫既人民，點樣先可以說服國際香港唔係疫埠呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a>"},{"pid":"a495eb534dcc13e7cc4142b179227a7b13b4cc97","tid":1844293,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:38:21.000Z","msg":"早就應該坐<br />\n<br />\n【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ABcOV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ABcOV7.jpg&h=0f21f561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鑑於中國肺炎疫症嚴峻，港共政府倒行逆施，徹底失去民意信任，已經無力領導現今疫症。<br />\n加上此疫症已經在香港鄰近地區面臨失控下，有機會令香港國家陷入危機，影響香港國家存亡。<br />\n<br />\n為防止中國肺炎在香港大規模爆發，在此宣佈，於香港時間2020年1月26日21時30分正式頒布緊急狀態令<br />\n為免錯過對抗中國肺炎黃金機會，全體連登網民會即時接管香港權力，全力帶領香港國民對抗中國肺炎，以 香港國民福祉為依歸。<br />\n請各位緊記，香港國家一切權力屬於人民，港共政權並非必然行使權力者。<br />\n<br />\n所有重大事件及決策，將會於連登討論區「政事台」討論及表決<br />\n議案帖文將會以【議案】為首以作識別<br />\n<br />\n大多數民意支持，以及正評數量淨值為1000或以上， 該議案會被視作「獲得通過」<br />\n<br />\n正式實現全民參政，全民議政<br />\n議案通過後，將運用全體公民力量及權力，以及民間一切可能的方法實行各種政策 。<br />\n請各位再次緊記，港共政權並非必然行使權力者，權力永遠歸於所有香港國民。<br />\n<br />\n【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844124</a>"},{"pid":"509987aae64893fc7a0249686ef0177740c5484c","tid":1844293,"uid":342268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"咁咪又係要醫好佢先有得佢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337e6f7055778ad8dff226ea498aaf8b44158145","tid":1844293,"uid":144001,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"141c69b83f3b3b49502f96868d5a7f634f9f72a6","tid":1844293,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲大陸人去醫院醫肺炎<br />\n又要瞞撚住自己冇肺炎<br />\n個腦係咪裝屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:49:20.000Z","msg":"直接死刑打毒針"},{"pid":"77a38b67d459ad5581d73a2d4f19d20e056518ca","tid":1844293,"uid":152976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:51:53.000Z","msg":"應該要判死刑 隱瞞病情=蓄意謀殺一堆人 <br />\n但先扣留48個鐘先"},{"pid":"52ed20d4c36f35734bdbc62cfd5d5b4e51c4998e","tid":1844293,"uid":235278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:13:12.000Z","msg":"應該直接燒咗佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7918b7c357111351469b2e31ee0e7a4fd63f0835","tid":1844293,"uid":121562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77a38b67d459ad5581d73a2d4f19d20e056518ca","tid":1844293,"uid":152976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:51:53.000Z","msg":"應該要判死刑 隱瞞病情=蓄意謀殺一堆人 <br />\n但先扣留48個鐘先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:52:02.000Z","msg":"有冇名單?<br />\n佢地唔好以為可以冇後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4b24c7343f7dbc7